Package com.rohitsood.urlybird.gui.record

Class Summary
GoButtonActionListener When the user clicks the Go button in the Manage Record window this listener is invoked.
GoPanel User interface component that allows the user to enter a record id and hit a 'Go' button.
ManageRecordButtonActionListener Listens for all actions on the manage record button panel of the Manage Record window.
ManageRecordButtonPanel Provides buttons for the user to interact with the record.
ManageRecordDataPanel Creates the panel to hold the user interface which lets the agent manage the room records.
ManageRecordInternalFrame This singleton JInternalFrame enables the administrator to search for entire records based on record id.
ManageRecordMenuItem The manage record menu item triggers a call to open the manage record internal frame.
ManageRecordMenuItemActionListener This ActionListener implementation listens to user action on the ManageRecordMenuItem.
RecordMenu The menu for all major day-to-day functionality of the booking agent.
